{
  "stem": "19441.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had all the nationality.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had Russian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had-- I had one Russian village with children, babies, and, and that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They was very good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very good to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the commander, when he picked me, so he said, you are a kindergarten teacher, so you will be looking after them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I said, if I have to look after them, then I don't want them to be on the roll call.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I want them to be able to be going to the sauna to be washed and to bathe, and I want them to have SS food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I thought, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He's going to give me a, a flap.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, you have-- you will have it all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When the Russian girls found out-- Russian women-- went out, because the women from-- till 30, they been in a different barrack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they saw they are heaven, what I provided them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they carried me all around that would take you to [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But anyway, in the future they did repay me many times what I did for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyway, so I had the Russian, I had the Polish, I had a Czech, I had a French, I had the mix marriages with children, and then I had the barracks with-- with Dutch girls, the Belgium girls, what-- Polish girl.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I said--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the Czech, the Polish, the Russian, they, they was all non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "French, yeah, non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only small group was the French, but the rest, there was thousands.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Clerical worker.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
